snippet.title: Mr. Prepper - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
☛ Wishlist Mr. Prepper on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/761830

Mr. Prepper is about to be preppered. You know something is wrong, the risk of a nuclear war is in the air and you need to be prepared for what's coming. They promised freedom but dealing with your paranoid government is just another day in this survival crafting game.
